CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh"...In the photos top, left to right; Vivian Weaver, Cleveland; Adelaide De Frantz, New York; Jayne Wood[son], Washington; Jean Wilkins, Albany...- Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Debs About Town members from left: Vivian Weaver, Adelaide De Frantz, Jayne Lewis Woodson, and Jean Wilkins, on porch of Loendi Club
